Project Description
This project is an add on for Project Mayhem that allows users to control Virtual DJ through the reactions

This project was created for the Project Mayhem Competition. In order to be able to use it, you need to have the following:
- Mayhem Remote Application
- Virtual DJ
- Virtual DJ must have the key mapper set that is included with all other files

The add on allows one to control Virtual DJ through the Mayhem APIs
